http://seadas.gsfc.nasa.gov/obtaining.html

Obtaining SeaDAS 4.1

   SeaDAS is available for download via anonymous FTP from
   seadas.gsfc.nasa.gov. To connect to the SeaDAS ftp site and to download
   those files, click here. The /seadas directory contains the following
   compressed tar files. The completed SeaDAS installation will require
   about 330MB without demo files and 950 MB with demo files. Using the
   embedded IDL runtime feature will add an additional 180MB to the
   installation.

   Required:
    1. SeaDAS source and executable files (~91MB) (select one of the
       following files that match or close to the OS of your workstation)
          + seadas_irix6.3.tar.gz or seadas_irix6.5.tar.gz: for SGI
            workstation
          + seadas_solaris2.6.tar.gz or seadas_solaris2.7.tar.gz: for SUN
            workstation
          + seadas_linux6.tar.gz or seadas_linux7.tar.gz for PC
    2. Data files for basic SeaDAS functions (~86MB)
          + seadas_data1.tar.gz

   Required only for SeaWiFS & OCTS processing: (~126MB)
     * seadas_data2.tar.gz

   Required for the embedded IDL runtime license feature (~130MB)
     * seadas_idl_rt.tar.gz

   Required only for CZCS processing: (~853MB)
     * seadas_data3.tar.gz

   Optional: optional sample data files and demo scripts for running the
   tutorial examples and demos. A complete suite of SeaWiFS products is
   included here. (~623MB)
     * seadas_demo.tar.gz

   Note: Some users, especially outside the U.S. have had trouble with the
   size of these files. We have split these files into smaller sections
   using the UNIX "split -12000" command. The split files can be found
   under the ./split directory.

   To put the pieces back together (concatenate the files), use the
   following commands:
   cat seadas_irix6.3.tar.gz?? > seadas_irix6.3.tar.gz (for seadas tar
   file), OR
   cat seadas_data1.tar.gz?? > seadas_data1.tar.gz (for data tar file)

   To put the pieces back together, uncompress them, and unTAR the TAR
   file in one step:
   cat seadas_irix6.3.tar.gz?? | gunzip -c - | tar xvf - (for source
   files) OR
   cat seadas_data1.tar.gz?? | gunzip -c - | tar xvf - (for data files)

   We can also create SeaDAS on CD for those users who do not have
   internet access. Please send your request to
   seadas@seadas.gsfc.nasa.gov.

   For installation instructions, please follow the simple steps in
   HOWTO_INSTALL.
